### POST /auth/login

Authenticate user and obtain JWT tokens.

**Request:**
```json
{
  "email": "user@metro.example",
  "password": "********"
}
```

**Response (200):**
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "data": {
    "accessToken": "eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIs...",
